                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070218-61-off318 t18070218-61-cd319"></join>, a gown, value 14 s. a cloak, value 20 s. a shawl, value 5 s. a shift, value 3 s. and one window curtain, value 10 d. the property of 
                     
